name: Decago-Pentagon Patterns
description:
اكتشف الأشكال المخفية
A multitude of patterns obtained by simply scaling an repeated arrangement of pentagon placed on a decagon. With the animated interpolation. This exploration is inspired by Islamic geometry.  The 8 second pauses are not several identical static frames but are encoded in the gif using this technique I demonstrate in this youtube video : http://bit.ly/2Ifl5k9 | Originally Made 02-08-20 | new 1080x1080 output
